OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTheatres refused McDonagh  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fplays over language        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The playwright Martin McDonagh has said
OL,6, theatres have refused to revive his    
OL,7, work because he would not allow changes
OL,8, to the language.                       
OL,10,FHe blames "petty outrage" for some     
OL,11,Fvenues wanting to make his plays more  
OL,12,F"palatable".                           
OL,14,FIt is a "major problem", he told BBC   
OL,15,FRadio 4's Today, and a "dangerous      
OL,16,Fplace" for writers.                    
OL,18,FMcDonagh's film The Banshees of        
OL,19,FInisherin was nominated for nine Oscars
OL,20,Fearlier this year.                     
